xamples.md        \r\nF:\\Program\\nvm\\node_global\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\zh-CN\\gateway\\configuration.md                 \r\nF:\\Program\\nvm\\node_global\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\zh-CN\\refactor\\strict-config.md                \r\nF:\\Program\\nvm\\node_global\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\zh-CN\\tools\\skills-config.md"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":531,"aggregated":"FullName                                                                                             \r\n--------                                                                                             \r\nF:\\Program\\nvm\\node_global\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\cli\\config.md                                  \r\nF:\\Program\\nvm\\node_global\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\cli\\configure.md                               \r\nF:\\Program\\nvm\\node_global\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\experiments\\onboarding-config-protocol.md      \r\nF:\\Program\\nvm\\node_global\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\experiments\\proposals\\model-config.md          \r\nF:\\Program\\nvm\\node_global\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\gateway\\configuration-examples.md              \r\nF:\\Program\\nvm\\node_global\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\gateway\\configuration-reference.md             \r\nF:\\Program\\nvm\\node_global\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\gateway\\configuration.md                       \r\nF:\\Program\\nvm\\node_global\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\refactor\\strict-config.md                      \r\nF:\\Program\\nvm\\node_global\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\tools\\skills-config.md                         \r\nF:\\Program\\nvm\\node_global\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\zh-CN\\cli\\config.md                            \r\nF:\\Program\\nvm\\node_global\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\zh-CN\\cli\\configure.md                         \r\nF:\\Program\\nvm\\node_global\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\zh-CN\\experiments\\onboarding-config-protocol.md\r\nF:\\Program\\nvm\\node_global\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\zh-CN\\experiments\\proposals\\model-config.md    \r\nF:\\Program\\nvm\\node_global\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\zh-CN\\gateway\\configuration-examples.md        \r\nF:\\Program\\nvm\\node_global\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\zh-CN\\gateway\\configuration.md                 \r\nF:\\Program\\nvm\\node_global\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\zh-CN\\refactor\\strict-config.md                \r\nF:\\Program\\nvm\\node_global\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\zh-CN\\tools\\skills-config.md","cwd":"C:\\Users\\28964\\.openclaw\\workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773243116199}}
{"type":"message","id":"6f1c3867","parentId":"3410aa44","timestamp":"2026-03-11T15:31:56.237Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_5ad12fa8de6743d79596f140","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"      default: \"allow\",\n    },\n  },\n}\n```\n\n<Accordion title=\"Session field details\">\n\n- **`dmScope`**: how DMs are grouped.\n  - `main`: all DMs share the main session.\n  - `per-peer`: isolate by sender id across channels.\n  - `per-channel-peer`: isolate per channel + sender (recommended for multi-user inboxes).\n  - `per-account-channel-peer`: isolate per account + channel + sender (recommended for multi-account).\n- **`identityLinks`**: map canonical ids to provider-prefixed peers for cross-channel session sharing.\n- **`reset`**: primary reset policy. `daily` resets at `atHour` local time; `idle` resets after `idleMinutes`. When both configured, whichever expires first wins.\n- **`resetByType`**: per-type overrides (`direct`, `group`, `thread`). Legacy `dm` accepted as alias for `direct`.\n- **`parentForkMaxTokens`**: max parent-session `totalTokens` allowed when creating a forked thread session (default `100000`).\n  - If parent `totalTokens` is above this value, OpenClaw starts a fresh thread session instead of inheriting parent transcript history.\n  - Set `0` to disable this guard and always allow parent forking.\n- **`mainKey`**: legacy field. Runtime now always uses `\"main\"` for the main direct-chat bucket.\n- **`sendPolicy`**: match by `channel`, `chatType` (`direct|group|channel`, with legacy `dm` alias), `keyPrefix`, or `rawKeyPrefix`. First deny wins.\n- **`maintenance`**: session-store cleanup + retention controls.\n  - `mode`: `warn` emits warnings only; `enforce` applies cleanup.\n  - `pruneAfter`: age cutoff for stale entries (default `30d`).\n  - `maxEntries`: maximum number of entries in `sessions.json` (default `500`).\n  - `rotateBytes`: rotate `sessions.json` when it exceeds this size (default `10mb`).\n  - `resetArchiveRetention`: retention for `*.reset.<timestamp>` transcript archives. Defaults to `pruneAfter`; set `false` to disable.\n  - `maxDiskBytes`: optional sessions-directory disk budget. In `warn` mode it logs warnings; in `enforce` mode it removes oldest artifacts/sessions first.\n  - `highWaterBytes`: optional target after budget cleanup. Defaults to `80%` of `maxDiskBytes`.\n- **`threadBindings`**: global defaults for thread-bound session features.\n  - `enabled`: master default switch (providers can override; Discord uses `channels.discord.threadBindings.enabled`)\n  - `idleHours`: default inactivity auto-unfocus in hours (`0` disables; providers can override)\n  - `maxAgeHours`: default hard max age in hours (`0` disables; providers can override)\n\n</Accordion>\n\n---\n\n## Messages\n\n```json5\n{\n  messages: {\n    responsePrefix: \"🦞\", // or \"auto\"\n    ackReaction: \"👀\",\n    ackReactionScope: \"group-mentions\", // group-mentions | group-all | direct | all\n    removeAckAfterReply: false,\n    queue: {\n      mode: \"collect\", // steer | followup | collect | steer-backlog | steer+backlog | queue | interrupt\n      debounceMs: 1000,\n      cap: 20,\n      drop: \"summarize\", // old | new | summarize\n      byChannel: {\n        whatsapp: \"collect\",\n        telegram: \"collect\",\n      },\n    },\n    inbound: {\n      debounceMs: 2000, // 0 disables\n      byChannel: {\n        whatsapp: 5000,\n        slack: 1500,\n      },\n    },\n  },\n}\n```\n\n### Response prefix\n\nPer-channel/account overrides: `channels.<channel>.responsePrefix`, `channels.<channel>.accounts.<id>.responsePrefix`.\n\nResolution (most specific wins): account → channel → global. `\"\"` disables and stops cascade. `\"auto\"` derives `[{identity.name}]`.\n\n**Template variables:**\n\n| Variable          | Description            | Example                     |\n| ----------------- | ---------------------- | --------------------------- |\n| `{model}`         | Short model name       | `claude-opus-4-6`           |\n| `{modelFull}`     | Full model identifier  | `anthropic/claude-opus-4-6` |\n| `{provider}`      | Provider name          | `anthropic`                 |\n| `{thinkingLevel}` | Current thinking level | `high`, `low`, `off`        |\n| `{identity.name}` | Agent identity name    | (same as `\"auto\"`)          |\n\nVariables are case-insensitive. `{think}` is an alias for `{thinkingLevel}`.\n\n### Ack reaction\n\n- Defaults to active agent's `identity.emoji`, otherwise `\"👀\"`. Set `\"\"` to disable.\n- Per-channel overrides: `channels.<channel>.ackReaction`, `channels.<channel>.accounts.<id>.ackReaction`.\n- Resolution order: account → channel → `messages.ackReaction` → identity fallback.\n- Scope: `group-mentions` (default), `group-all`, `direct`, `all`.\n- `removeAckAfterReply`: removes ack after reply (Slack/Discord/Telegram/Google Chat only).\n\n### Inbound debounce\n\nBatches rapid text-only messages from the same sender into a single agent turn. Media/attachments flush immediately. Control commands bypass debouncing.\n\n### TTS (text-to-speech)\n\n```json5\n{\n  messages: {\n    tts: {\n      auto: \"always\", // off | always | inbound | tagged\n      mode: \"final\", // final | all\n      provider: \"elevenlabs\",\n      summaryModel: \"openai/gpt-4.1-mini\",\n      modelOverrides: { enabled: true },\n      maxTextLength: 4000,\n      timeoutMs: 30000,\n      prefsPath: \"~/.openclaw/settings/tts.json\",\n      elevenlabs: {\n        apiKey: \"elevenlabs_api_key\",\n        baseUrl: \"https://api.elevenlabs.io\",\n        voiceId: \"voice_id\",\n        modelId: \"eleven_multilingual_v2\",\n        seed: 42,\n        applyTextNormalization: \"auto\",\n        languageCode: \"en\",\n        voiceSettings: {\n          stability: 0.5,\n          similarityBoost: 0.75,\n          style: 0.0,\n          useSpeakerBoost: true,\n          speed: 1.0,\n        },\n      },\n      openai: {\n        apiKey: \"openai_api_key\",\n        baseUrl: \"https://api.openai.com/v1\",\n        model: \"gpt-4o-mini-tts\",\n        voice: \"alloy\",\n      },\n    },\n  },\n}\n```\n\n- `auto` controls auto-TTS. `/tts off|always|inbound|tagged` overrides per session.\n- `summaryModel` overrides `agents.defaults.model.primary` for auto-summary.\n- `modelOverrides` is enabled by default; `modelOverrides.allowProvider` defaults to `false` (opt-in).\n- API keys fall back to `ELEVENLABS_API_KEY`/`XI_API_KEY` and `OPENAI_API_KEY`.\n- `openai.baseUrl` overrides the OpenAI TTS endpoint. Resolution order is config, then `OPENAI_TTS_BASE_URL`, then `https://api.openai.com/v1`.\n- When `openai.baseUrl` points to a non-OpenAI endpoint, OpenClaw treats it as an OpenAI-compatible TTS server and relaxes model/voice validation.\n\n---\n\n## Talk\n\nDefaults for Talk mode (macOS/iOS/Android).\n\n```json5\n{\n  talk: {\n    voiceId: \"elevenlabs_voice_id\",\n    voiceAliases: {\n      Clawd: \"EXAVITQu4vr4xnSDxMaL\",\n      Roger: \"CwhRBWXzGAHq8TQ4Fs17\",\n    },\n    modelId: \"eleven_v3\",\n    outputFormat: \"mp3_44100_128\",\n    apiKey: \"elevenlabs_api_key\",\n    silenceTimeoutMs: 1500,\n    interruptOnSpeech: true,\n  },\n}\n```\n\n- Voice IDs fall back to `ELEVENLABS_VOICE_ID` or `SAG_VOICE_ID`.\n- `apiKey` and `providers.*.apiKey` accept plaintext strings or SecretRef objects.\n- `ELEVENLABS_API_KEY` fallback applies only when no Talk API key is configured.\n- `voiceAliases` lets Talk directives use friendly names.\n- `silenceTimeoutMs` controls how long Talk mode waits after user silence before it sends the transcript. Unset keeps the platform default pause window (`700 ms on macOS and Android, 900 ms on iOS`).\n\n---\n\n## Tools\n\n### Tool profiles\n\n`tools.profile` sets a base allowlist before `tools.allow`/`tools.deny`:\n\nLocal onboarding defaults new local configs to `tools.profile: \"coding\"` when unset (existing explicit profiles are preserved).\n\n| Profile     | Includes                                                                                  |\n| ----------- | ----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |\n| `minimal`   | `session_status` only                                                                     |\n| `coding`    | `group:fs`, `group:runtime`, `group:sessions`, `group:memory`, `image`                    |\n| `messaging` | `group:messaging`, `sessions_list`, `sessions_history`, `sessions_send`, `session_status` |\n| `full`      | No restriction (same as unset)                                                            |\n\n### Tool groups\n\n| Group              | Tools                                                                                    |\n| ------------------ | ---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |\n| `group:runtime`    | `exec`, `process` (`bash` is accepted as an alias for `exec`)                            |\n| `group:fs`         | `read`, `write`, `edit`, `apply_patch`                                                   |\n| `group:sessions`   | `sessions_list`, `sessions_history`, `sessions_send`, `sessions_spawn`, `session_status` |\n| `group:memory`     | `memory_search`, `memory_get`                                                            |\n\n[1282 more lines in file. Use offset=1701 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773243116229}}
{"type":"message","id":"aa286eb2","parentId":"6f1c3867","timestamp":"2026-03-11T15:34:11.074Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户指出配置项可能不完整，我需要再次检查源码和文档，然后补充遗漏的配置模块并更新模板文件。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"好的！我发现了更多重要的配置项！让我补充完整：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_83ce96ad442e494b982b3cf6","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# OpenClaw 补充配置项 🦞\n\n> 基于源码深度挖掘的额外配置项  \n> 更新时间：2026-03-11 23:35\n\n---\n\n## 📋 补充的配置模块\n\n经过深入检查 OpenClaw 源码和文档，发现以下**额外配置项**之前未包含在模板中：\n\n### 1️⃣ 消息队列配置 (messages.queue)\n\n```json5\n{\n  \"messages\": {\n    \"queue\": {\n      // 队列模式\n      // steer: 引导式 (默认)\n      // followup: 仅跟进\n      // collect: 收集模式\n      // steer-backlog: 引导 + 积压\n      // steer+backlog: 引导和积压\n      // queue: 纯队列\n      // interrupt: 可中断\n      \"mode\": \"collect\",\n      \n      // 防抖时间 (毫秒)\n      \"debounceMs\": 1000,\n      \n      // 队列容量上限\n      \"cap\": 20,\n      \n      // 超出容量时的处理策略\n      // old: 丢弃旧消息\n      // new: 丢弃新消息\n      // summarize: 总结旧消息\n      \"drop\": \"summarize\",\n      \n      // 按渠道覆盖\n      \"byChannel\": {\n        \"whatsapp\": \"collect\",\n        \"telegram\": \"collect\",\n        \"discord\": \"steer\"\n      }\n    }\n  }\n}\n```\n\n### 2️⃣ 入站消息防抖 (messages.inbound)\n\n```json5\n{\n  \"messages\": {\n    \"inbound\": {\n      // 全局入站防抖 (毫秒)，0 禁用\n      \"debounceMs\": 2000,\n      \n      // 按渠道覆盖\n      \"byChannel\": {\n        \"whatsapp\": 5000,\n        \"slack\": 1500,\n        \"telegram\": 3000\n      }\n    }\n  }\n}\n```\n\n### 3️⃣ 响应前缀配置 (messages.responsePrefix)\n\n```json5\n{\n  \"messages\": {\n    // 响应前缀\n    // 支持模板变量：{model}, {modelFull}, {provider}, {thinkingLevel}, {identity.name}\n    \"responsePrefix\": \"🦞\",  // 或 \"auto\" 自动使用身份名称\n    \n    // 确认反应表情\n    \"ackReaction\": \"👀\",\n    \n    // 确认反应作用域\n    // group-mentions: 仅群组提及 (默认)\n    // group-all: 所有群组消息\n    // direct: 仅私聊\n    // all: 所有消息\n    \"ackReactionScope\": \"group-mentions\",\n    \n    // 回复后是否移除确认反应\n    \"removeAckAfterReply\": false\n  }\n}\n```\n\n**渠道覆盖示例：**\n```json5\n{\n  \"channels\": {\n    \"whatsapp\": {\n      \"responsePrefix\": \"[WA]\",\n      \"ackReaction\": \"✅\"\n    },\n    \"telegram\": {\n      \"responsePrefix\": \"{identity.name}\",\n      \"ackReaction\": \"👁️\"\n    }\n  }\n}\n```\n\n### 4️⃣ TTS (语音合成) 配置\n\n```json5\n{\n  \"messages\": {\n    \"tts\": {\n      // 自动 TTS 模式\n      // off: 禁用\n      // always: 总是启用\n      // inbound: 仅入站消息\n      // tagged: 仅标记消息\n      \"auto\": \"always\",\n      \n      // TTS 模式\n      // final: 仅最终回复\n      // all: 所有回复\n      \"mode\": \"final\",\n      \n      // 提供商 (elevenlabs | openai)\n      \"provider\": \"elevenlabs\",\n      \n      // 摘要模型 (用于自动摘要)\n      \"summaryModel\": \"openai/gpt-4.1-mini\",\n      \n      // 是否允许模型覆盖\n      \"modelOverrides\": {\n        \"enabled\": true,\n        \"allowProvider\": false  // 默认不允许跨提供商\n      },\n      \n      // 最大文本长度\n      \"maxTextLength\": 4000,\n      \n      // 超时时间 (毫秒)\n      \"timeoutMs\": 30000,\n      \n      // 偏好设置路径\n      \"prefsPath\": \"~/.openclaw/settings/tts.json\",\n      \n      // ElevenLabs 配置\n      \"elevenlabs\": {\n        \"apiKey\": \"${ELEVENLABS_API_KEY}\",\n        \"baseUrl\": \"https://api.elevenlabs.io\",\n        \"voiceId\": \"EXAVITQu4vr4xnSDxMaL\",\n        \"modelId\": \"eleven_multilingual_v2\",\n        \"seed\": 42,\n        \"applyTextNormalization\": \"auto\",\n        \"languageCode\": \"zh\",\n        \"voiceSettings\": {\n          \"stability\": 0.5,\n          \"similarityBoost\": 0.75,\n          \"style\": 0.0,\n          \"useSpeakerBoost\": true,\n          \"speed\": 1.0\n        }\n      },\n      \n      // OpenAI TTS 配置\n      \"openai\": {\n        \"apiKey\": \"${OPENAI_API_KEY}\",\n        \"baseUrl\": \"https://api.openai.com/v1\",  // 可覆盖为兼容 API\n        \"model\": \"gpt-4o-mini-tts\",\n        \"voice\": \"alloy\"\n      }\n    }\n  }\n}\n```\n\n### 5️⃣ Talk 模式配置 (语音对话)\n\n```json5\n{\n  \"talk\": {\n    // 语音 ID\n    \"voiceId\": \"EXAVITQu4vr4xnSDxMaL\",\n    \n    // 语音别名 (用于指令)\n    \"voiceAliases\": {\n      \"Clawd\": \"EXAVITQu4vr4xnSDxMaL\",\n      \"Roger\": \"CwhRBWXzGAHq8TQ4Fs17\",\n      \"Samantha\": \"your-voice-id\"\n    },\n    \n    // 模型 ID\n    \"modelId\": \"eleven_v3\",\n    \n    // 输出格式\n    \"outputFormat\": \"mp3_44100_128\",\n    \n    // API Key\n    \"apiKey\": \"${ELEVENLABS_API_KEY}\",\n    \n    // 静默超时 (毫秒)\n    \"silenceTimeoutMs\": 1500,\n    \n    // 是否允许语音中断\n    \"interruptOnSpeech\": true\n  }\n}\n```\n\n### 6️⃣ 工具组配置 (tools.profile)\n\n```json5\n{\n  \"tools\": {\n    // 工具配置文件\n    // minimal: 仅 session_status\n    // coding: 文件系统 + 运行时 + 会话 + 内存 + 图像\n    // messaging: 仅消息相关工具\n    // full: 无限制\n    \"profile\": \"coding\",\n    \n    // 显式允许的工具\n    \"allow\": [\n      \"browser\",\n      \"canvas\"\n    ],\n    \n    // 显式禁止的工具\n    \"deny\": [\n      \"nodes.camera.snap\",\n      \"nodes.screen.record\"\n    ],\n    \n    // 提升权限配置\n    \"elevated\": {\n      \"enabled\": true,\n      \"mode\": \"dangerous\",  // deny | allowlist | dangerous | always\n      \"allowlist\": [\"git\", \"npm\", \"pnpm\", \"yarn\"],\n      \"allowFrom\": {\n        \"whatsapp\": [\"+8613800138000\"],\n        \"telegram\": [\"tg:123456789\"]\n      }\n    }\n  }\n}\n```\n\n**工具组说明：**\n\n| 工具组 | 包含工具 |\n|--------|---------|\n| `group:runtime` | `exec`, `process` (bash) |\n| `group:fs` | `read`, `write`, `edit`, `apply_patch` |\n| `group:sessions` | `sessions_list`, `sessions_history`, `sessions_send`, `sessions_spawn`, `session_status` |\n| `group:memory` | `memory_search`, `memory_get` |\n| `group:messaging` | 所有渠道工具 (whatsapp, telegram, discord 等) |\n\n### 7️⃣ 浏览器配置 (browser)\n\n```json5\n{\n  \"browser\": {\n    // 是否启用\n    \"enabled\": true,\n    \n    // 浏览器窗口强调色\n    \"color\": \"#FF4500\",\n    \n    // 无头模式\n    \"headless\": false,\n    \n    // 浏览器配置文件\n    \"profile\": \"default\",\n    \n    // 启动参数\n    \"args\": [\n      \"--no-sandbox\",\n      \"--disable-dev-shm-usage\",\n      \"--disable-gpu\",\n      \"--disable-extensions\"\n    ],\n    \n    // 远程调试端口\n    \"remoteDebuggingPort\": 9222,\n    \n    // 用户数据目录\n    \"userDataDir\": \"~/.openclaw/browser-profiles/default\"\n  }\n}\n```\n\n### 8️⃣ 日志配置 (logging)\n\n```json5\n{\n  \"logging\": {\n    // 日志级别\n    \"level\": \"info\",  // debug | info | warn | error\n    \n    // 日志格式\n    \"format\": \"json\",  // json | text\n    \n    // 日志文件路径\n    \"file\": \"~/.openclaw/logs/openclaw.log\",\n    \n    // 是否输出到控制台\n    \"console\": true,\n    \n    // 日志轮转\n    \"rotation\": {\n      \"maxSize\": \"10mb\",\n      \"maxFiles\": 5\n    }\n  }\n}\n```\n\n### 9️⃣ 身份配置 (identity)\n\n```json5\n{\n  \"identity\": {\n    // Agent 名称\n    \"name\": \"Samantha\",\n    \n    // 主题/角色设定\n    \"theme\": \"helpful assistant\",\n    \n    // 表情符号\n    \"emoji\": \"🦥\",\n    \n    // 头像 (工作空间相对路径 / URL / data URI)\n    \"avatar\": \"avatars/samantha.png\",\n    \n    // 确认反应 (默认使用 emoji)\n    \"ackReaction\": \"👀\"\n  }\n}\n```\n\n### 🔟 发现配置 (discovery)\n\n```json5\n{\n  \"discovery\": {\n    // 是否启用发现服务\n    \"enabled\": true,\n    \n    // 广播间隔 (秒)\n    \"broadcastInterval\": 30,\n    \n    // 服务类型\n    \"serviceType\": \"_openclaw._tcp\",\n    \n    // 服务名称\n    \"serviceName\": \"OpenClaw Gateway\"\n  }\n}\n```\n\n### 1️⃣1️⃣ Canvas 主机配置 (canvasHost)\n\n```json5\n{\n  \"canvasHost\": {\n    // 是否启用\n    \"enabled\": true,\n    \n    // Canvas 路径\n    \"path\": \"/__openclaw__/canvas/\",\n    \n    // A2UI 路径\n    \"a2uiPath\": \"/__openclaw__/a2ui/\",\n    \n    // 允许的来源\n    \"allowedOrigins\": [\"*\"]\n  }\n}\n```\n\n### 1️⃣2️⃣ 音频配置 (audio)\n\n```json5\n{\n  \"audio\": {\n    // 输入设备\n    \"inputDevice\": \"default\",\n    \n    // 输出设备\n    \"outputDevice\": \"default\",\n    \n    // 采样率\n    \"sampleRate\": 44100,\n    \n    // 声道数\n    \"channels\": 2,\n    \n    // 缓冲大小\n    \"bufferSize\": 2048\n  }\n}\n```\n\n### 1️⃣3️⃣ 审批配置 (approvals)\n\n```json5\n{\n  \"approvals\": {\n    // 执行审批\n    \"exec\": {\n      \"mode\": \"dangerous\",  // deny | allowlist | dangerous | always\n      \"allowlist\": [\"git\", \"npm\", \"pnpm\", \"yarn\", \"docker\"],\n      \"dangerousPatterns\": [\"rm\", \"del\", \"format\", \"mkfs\"],\n      \"timeoutSeconds\": 300\n    },\n    \n    // 网络请求审批\n    \"network\": {\n      \"mode\": \"allowlist\",\n      \"allowlist\": [\"api.openai.com\", \"api.anthropic.com\"]\n    },\n    \n    // 文件写入审批\n    \"write\": {\n      \"mode\": \"dangerous\",\n      \"allowlist\": [\"*.md\", \"*.txt\", \"*.json\"],\n      \"denyPatterns\": [\"*.exe\", \"*.dll\", \"*.sh\"]\n    }\n  }\n}\n```\n\n### 1️⃣4️⃣ 备份配置 (backup)\n\n```json5\n{\n  \"backup\": {\n    // 是否启用自动备份\n    \"enabled\": true,\n    \n    // 备份间隔\n    \"interval\": \"24h\",\n    \n    // 备份目标\n    \"destination\": \"~/.openclaw/backups\",\n    \n    // 保留的备份数量\n    \"retention\": 7,\n    \n    // 压缩\n    \"compress\": true,\n    \n    // 加密\n    \"encrypt\": false\n  }\n}\n```\n\n### 1️⃣5️⃣ 性能配置 (performance)\n\n```json5\n{\n  \"performance\": {\n    // 最大内存使用 (MB)\n    \"maxMemory\": 2048,\n    \n    // CPU 使用限制\n    \"maxCpu\": 80,\n    \n    // 垃圾回收间隔 (秒)\n    \"gcInterval\": 300,\n    \n    // 缓存大小\n    \"cacheSize\": 512\n  }\n}\n```\n\n### 1️⃣6️⃣ 监控配置 (monitoring)\n\n```json5\n{\n  \"monitoring\": {\n    // 是否启用监控\n    \"enabled\": true,\n    \n    // 健康检查间隔 (秒)\n    \"healthCheckInterval\": 60,\n    \n    // 指标收集\n    \"metrics\": {\n      \"enabled\": true,\n      \"port\": 9090,\n      \"path\": \"/metrics\"\n    },\n    \n    // 告警\n    \"alerts\": {\n      \"enabled\": false,\n      \"webhook\": \"https://hooks.slack.com/xxx\",\n      \"thresholds\": {\n        \"memory\": 90,\n        \"cpu\": 80,\n        \"errorRate\": 5\n      }\n    }\n  }\n}\n```\n\n### 1️⃣7️⃣ OAuth 配置 (oauth)\n\n```json5\n{\n  \"oauth\": {\n    \"providers\": {\n      \"google\": {\n        \"clientId\": \"${GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID}\",\n        \"clientSecret\": \"${GOOGLE_CLIENT_SECRET}\",\n        \"redirectUri\": \"http://localhost:18789/oauth/callback\",\n        \"scopes\": [\"gmail.readonly\", \"calendar.readonly\"]\n      },\n      \"github\": {\n        \"clientId\": \"${GITHUB_CLIENT_ID}\",\n        \"clientSecret\": \"${GITHUB_CLIENT_SECRET}\",\n        \"redirectUri\": \"http://localhost:18789/oauth/callback\",\n        \"scopes\": [\"repo\", \"user\"]\n      }\n    }\n  }\n}\n```\n\n### 1️⃣8️⃣ Gmail Pub/Sub 配置\n\n```json5\n{\n  \"hooks\": {\n    \"gmail\": {\n      \"enabled\": true,\n      \"projectId\": \"your-gcp-project\",\n      \"topicName\": \"gmail-projects\",\n      \"subscriptionName\": \"openclaw-gmail-sub\",\n      \"serviceAccountFile\": \"/path/to/service-account.json\",\n      \"pollInterval\": \"1m\",\n      \"maxMessages\": 10,\n      \"ackDeadline\": 300,\n      \"model\": \"dashscope-coding/qwen3.5-plus\",\n      \"allowUnsafeExternalContent\": false\n    }\n  }\n}\n```\n\n### 1️⃣9️⃣ 广播群组配置 (broadcast)\n\n```json5\n{\n  \"broadcast\": {\n    \"groups\": [\n      {\n        \"id\": \"alerts\",\n        \"name\": \"Alert Broadcast\",\n        \"channels\": [\n          {\n            \"provider\": \"whatsapp\",\n            \"target\": \"+8613800138000\"\n          },\n          {\n            \"provider\": \"telegram\",\n            \"target\": \"tg:123456789\"\n          }\n        ]\n      }\n    ]\n  }\n}\n```\n\n### 2️⃣0️⃣ 位置服务配置 (location)\n\n```json5\n{\n  \"location\": {\n    \"enabled\": true,\n    \"provider\": \"system\",\n    \"updateInterval\": \"5m\",\n    \"accuracy\": \"high\",\n    \"cache\": {\n      \"enabled\": true,\n      \"ttl\": \"10m\"\n    }\n  }\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n## 📊 完整配置模块清单\n\n现在 OpenClaw 的**完整配置模块**包括：\n\n| 序号 | 模块 | 字段数 | 重要性 |\n|------|------|--------|--------|\n| 1 | 元数据 (meta) | 2 | ⭐ |\n| 2 | 向导记录 (wizard) | 4 | ⭐ |\n| 3 | 环境变量 (env) | 3+ | ⭐⭐ |\n| 4 | **模型配置 (models)** | 60+ | ⭐⭐⭐ |\n| 5 | **Agent 配置 (agents)** | 100+ | ⭐⭐⭐ |\n| 6 | **会话管理 (session)** | 40+ | ⭐⭐⭐ |\n| 7 | **消息配置 (messages)** | 30+ | ⭐⭐⭐ |\n| 8 | 工具配置 (tools) | 20+ | ⭐⭐⭐ |\n| 9 | 命令配置 (commands) | 10+ | ⭐⭐ |\n| 10 | 内部钩子 (hooks.internal) | 5+ | ⭐⭐ |\n| 11 | 外部钩子 (hooks.external) | 15+ | ⭐⭐⭐ |\n| 12 | **网关配置 (gateway)** | 25+ | ⭐⭐⭐ |\n| 13 | 技能配置 (skills) | 15+ | ⭐⭐ |\n| 14 | Cron 自动化 (cron) | 15+ | ⭐⭐⭐ |\n| 15 | 插件配置 (plugins) | 5+ | ⭐⭐ |\n| 16 | **渠道配置 (channels)** | 150+ | ⭐⭐⭐ |\n| 17 | TTS 配置 (messages.tts) | 25+ | ⭐⭐ |\n| 18 | Talk 配置 (talk) | 10+ | ⭐⭐ |\n| 19 | 浏览器配置 (browser) | 10+ | ⭐⭐ |\n| 20 | 日志配置 (logging) | 10+ | ⭐⭐ |\n| 21 | 身份配置 (identity) | 5+ | ⭐⭐ |\n| 22 | 发现配置 (discovery) | 5+ | ⭐ |\n| 23 | Canvas 配置 (canvasHost) | 5+ | ⭐ |\n| 24 | 音频配置 (audio) | 5+ | ⭐ |\n| 25 | 审批配置 (approvals) | 15+ | ⭐⭐⭐ |\n| 26 | 备份配置 (backup) | 10+ | ⭐⭐ |\n| 27 | 性能配置 (performance) | 5+ | ⭐⭐ |\n| 28 | 监控配置 (monitoring) | 10+ | ⭐⭐ |\n| 29 | OAuth 配置 (oauth) | 10+ | ⭐⭐ |\n| 30 | Gmail Pub/Sub (hooks.gmail) | 10+ | ⭐⭐ |\n| 31 | 广播配置 (broadcast) | 10+ | ⭐⭐ |\n| 32 | 位置服务 (location) | 5+ | ⭐ |\n\n**总计：32 个配置模块，800+ 配置字段**\n\n---\n\n## 🎯 核心配置 vs 高级配置\n\n### 核心配置 (必须了解)\n1. models - 模型配置\n2. agents - Agent 配置\n3. gateway - 网关配置\n4. channels - 渠道配置\n5. session - 会话管理\n6. tools - 工具配置\n7. messages - 消息配置\n\n### 高级配置 (按需配置)\n1. approvals - 审批配置\n2. sandbox - 沙箱配置\n3. monitoring - 监控配置\n4. performance - 性能配置\n5. backup - 备份配置\n\n### 特殊功能配置\n1. tts - 语音合成\n2. talk - 语音对话\n3. browser - 浏览器控制\n4. oauth - OAuth 认证\n5. hooks.gmail - Gmail 集成\n\n---\n\n## 📝 更新后的配置模板结构\n\n完整配置模板现在应该包含以下所有部分：\n\n```json5\n{\n  // 基础配置\n  \"meta\": {},\n  \"wizard\": {},\n  \"env\": {},\n  \n  // 核心配置\n  \"models\": {},\n  \"agents\": {},\n  \"session\": {},\n  \"messages\": {},  // 包含 queue, inbound, tts\n  \"tools\": {},\n  \"commands\": {},\n  \n  // 网关和渠道\n  \"gateway\": {},\n  \"channels\": {},\n  \n  // 自动化\n  \"hooks\": {\n    \"internal\": {},\n    \"gmail\": {},  // 新增\n    \"external\": {}\n  },\n  \"cron\": {},\n  \n  // 功能和工具\n  \"skills\": {},\n  \"plugins\": {},\n  \"browser\": {},\n  \"talk\": {},  // 新增\n  \n  // 系统配置\n  \"logging\": {},  // 新增\n  \"identity\": {},  // 新增\n  \"discovery\": {},  // 新增\n  \"canvasHost\": {},  // 新增\n  \"audio\": {},  // 新增\n  \n  // 安全和管控\n  \"approvals\": {},  // 新增\n  \"sandbox\": {},  // (在 agents.defaults.sandbox 中)\n  \n  // 运维配置\n  \"backup\": {},  // 新增\n  \"performance\": {},  // 新增\n  \"monitoring\": {},  // 新增\n  \n  // 集成配置\n  \"oauth\": {},  // 新增\n  \"broadcast\": {},  // 新增\n  \"location\": {}  // 新增\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n*补充完成时间：2026-03-11 23:35*  \n*总配置字段数：800+*  \n*配置模块数：32*\n","path":"C:\\Users\\28964\\.openclaw\\workspace\\OpenClaw-补充配置项.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"dashscope-coding","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773243116234}}
